    "description": "HouseFreedom Co.,Ltd. engages in the sale of newly built detached houses in Japan. The company operates through Real Estate Brokerage, Newly Constructed House Sales, Construction Contract Work, Non-Life Insurance, and Real Estate Leasing segments. The Real Estate Brokerage segment engages in the real estate buying and selling, and brokerage and sales agency business. The Newly Constructed House Sales segment is involved in the sale of detached houses; and planning, development, construction, and sale of used properties. The Construction Contract Work segment engages in the custom-built housing and renovation contracting business. The Non-Life Insurance segment offers insurance agency services, such as fire and earthquake insurance. The Real Estate Leasing segment engages in the acquisition, development, leasing, and sale of residential apartments, office buildings, and other rental properties. HouseFreedom Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Matsubara, Japan."
